on (e.g., [[Internal Revenue Service]] [[501c3]] or equivalent) of the main body # tertiary = number of church-operated tertiary level colleges or universities # seminaries = number of church-operated seminaries # publications = names of the publications made by the denomination # other_names = alternative name or names by which the denomination is/was known # website = official website # website_title1 = alternative website title # website1 = alternative web address # slogan= Slogan # logo= Logo # module= Used for embedding other infoboxes into this one # footnotes = any footnotes
